source code for DRPS calculations in
Dynamical properties of two- and three-dimensional colloidal clusters
by B. FacÌŒkovec and J. W. R. Morgan and D. J. Wale

published in ...

directories:

2D ... data for 2D Morse cluster
3D ... data for 3D Morse cluster

subdirectories

DRPS ... files for solving the linear algebraic system of equations for discrete relaxation path sampling
KMC ... kinetic Monte Carlo on rate matrices
MD ... molecular dynamics propagation constrained to a cell
PTMC ... parallel tempering Monte Carlocc
structures ... scripts for structure identification
TST ... files for transition state theory calculation
